snippet.title: Arcade Game: Crash N Score (1975 Atari)
snippet.description:
A demolition derby game where a player tries to hit the pylon that pops into the screen at random and the action is frantic. 

Any interested in trying out this game, here it is:
http://adamulation.blogspot.com/
